 To ask a girl to marry you, you must first obtain her consent. This can be done by completeing the task known as “The ritual of engagement” with the help of a close friend. A ritual is an established custom, which people follow with the hope that the ritual will bring them luck and good fortune. With this in mind, it is important that you clearly state the following three things: 1. you would like to engage (marry) this woman 2. you
